# Agentic Workspace Integration Walkthrough

I have successfully implemented the **Workspace Explorer** feature in the `gemini-devtool-suite`. This addition transforms the dashboard into a more capable agentic environment by providing direct access to the local project structure.

## Key Accomplishments

- **Integrated File Explorer**: Added a high-fidelity workspace view that displays the local file system.
- **Dynamic Navigation**: Updated the sidebar and application routing to support the new Workspace view.
- **Real-time Synchronization**: Connected the UI to the backend `/api/files` endpoint for live workspace scanning.
- **Premium UI/UX**: Implemented a modern, dark-themed design with search functionality and intuitive file icons.

