## Technical Implementation Details

1.  **New Component**: [WorkspaceExplorer.tsx](file:///c:/Users/shoaib/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/gemini-devtool-suite/components/WorkspaceExplorer.tsx) handles state management for file fetching and filtering.
2.  **State Management**: Updated [View](file:///c:/Users/shoaib/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/gemini-devtool-suite/App.tsx#29-49) enum in [types.ts](file:///c:/Users/shoaib/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/gemini-devtool-suite/types.ts) and [App.tsx](file:///c:/Users/shoaib/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/gemini-devtool-suite/App.tsx) logic to manage the active view.
3.  **Theming**: Ensured full compatibility with both Light and Dark modes.

